---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 420
  - Title: Qur’ân
    Location: XLVII 12
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation=Atheism
---
Verily Allâh will bring those who believe and do good works into
gardens beneath which rivers flow; while those who disbelieve take
their comfort in this life and eat even as the cattle eat, and the
Fire is their habitation.
